data.title: 9INE snatch spot at ESL Pro League Season 17 Conference
data.description: The Poles clinched a place in the event after a full-distance, best-of-five grand final.

data.title: Heroic win Danish derby; punch ticket to BLAST Fall Final
data.description: Casper "cadiaN" Mller's side will play in front of their home crowd in the Royal Arena.

data.title: IEM Rio Major profile: Ninjas in Pyjamas
data.description: With a new AWPer, new in-game leader, new language, and former shotcaller and X-factor player looking unleashed, Ninjas in Pyjamas hope to continue their honeymoon phase in Rio.

data.title: Lynn Vision qualify for ESL Pro League Season 17 Conference
data.description: The Chinese roster won ESL Challenger League Season 42 Asia-Pacific to advance to the upcoming Maltese LAN.

data.title: IEM Rio Major profile: BIG
data.description: The German squad has been plagued by roster instability and heads into the Major with a stand-in, a tough predicament to make it out of the Challengers Stage alive.

data.title: CLG Red, EG Gold qualify for ESL Impact League Finals
data.description: The pair will be the two North American representatives at the $123,000 tournament taking place on November 25-27 in Sweden.

data.title: Fluxo, MIBR through to BLAST Showdown grand final; 00NATION out
data.description: Upsets continued in the brutal single-elimination bracket as Epitacio "TACO" de Melo's side have been eliminated by a face most familiar to them.

data.title: IEM Rio Major profile: IHC
data.description: The Mongolians head into their second Major as APAC's top side, but they are still far from a sure shot to make the Legends Stage as the second-lowest team in our power ranking.

data.title: Heroic best Sangal in Fall Showdown, set up all-Danish final versus Astralis
data.description: The two Danish sides will lock horns as they look to take home the sole spot up for grabs at the $425,000 Fall Final.

data.title: IEM Rio Major profile: FURIA
data.description: The hometown favorites for a playoff run head to Rio with a lot to prove.
